《'''小鎮滋味'''》（{{lang-en|''Santa Clarita Diet''}}）是一部由{{le|維克多·佛瑞斯可|Victor Fresco}}開創，於2017年2月3日在[[Netflix|Netflix]]開播的[[美國|美國]]恐怖喜劇，由[[茱兒·芭莉摩|茱兒·芭莉摩]]和[[蒂莫西·奥利芬特|提摩西·奧利芬]]主演。<ref name="deadline">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/drew-barrymore-timothy-olyphant-star-santa-clarita-diet-netflix-series-1201722867/|title=Drew Barrymore & Timothy Olyphant To Star In 'Santa Clarita Diet' Netflix Series|author=Nellie Andreeva|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|access-date=2017-02-05|archive-date=2019-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190111145354/https://deadline.com/2016/03/drew-barrymore-timothy-olyphant-star-santa-clarita-diet-netflix-series-1201722867/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 佛瑞斯可擔任節目統籌，並與芭莉摩、奧利芬、亞倫·凱普倫、翠西·卡茲奇、克里斯·米勒和安珀·處斯戴爾共同擔任執行製作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/drew-barrymore-timothy-olyphant-star-876795|title=Drew Barrymore, Timothy Olyphant to Star in Netflix Comedy Series 'Santa Clarita Diet'|author=Lesley Goldberg|work=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|access-date=2017-02-05|archive-date=2017-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209070921/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/drew-barrymore-timothy-olyphant-star-876795|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/11/28/netflix-santa-clarita-diet-premiere-date|title=Netflix sets premiere for Drew Barrymore comedy Santa Clarita Diet — exclusive|accessdate=2016-11-28|date=2016-11-28|last=Abrams|first=Natalie|website=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|archive-date=2018-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919222117/https://www.ew.com/article/2016/11/28/netflix-santa-clarita-diet-premiere-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年3月29日，Netflix宣布續訂第2季。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/03/santa-clarita-diet-renewed-season-2-drew-barrymire-netflix-1202054362/|title=Drew Barrymore Comedy ‘Santa Clarita Diet’ Renewed For Season 2 By Netflix|author=Nellie Andreeva|work=Deadline.com|access-date=2017-05-22|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116182824/https://deadline.com/2017/03/santa-clarita-diet-renewed-season-2-drew-barrymire-netflix-1202054362/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2018年5月8日，宣布續訂第3季，於2019年3月29日播放。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/05/santa-clarita-diet-renewed-season-3-netflix-1202384421/|title=‘Santa Clarita Diet’ Renewed For Season 3 By Netflix|author=Nellie Andreeva|work=Deadline.com|date=2018-05-08|accessdate=2018-05-08|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211214502/https://deadline.com/2018/05/santa-clarita-diet-renewed-season-3-netflix-1202384421/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年4月26日，本劇被取消<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://deadline.com/2019/04/santa-clarita-diet-canceled-netflix-three-seasons-1202602903/ |title = ‘Santa Clarita Diet’ Canceled By Netflix After 3 Seasons |author = Nellie Andreeva |date = 2019-04-26 |publisher = Deadline Hollywood |language = en |access-date = 2019-04-28 |archive-date = 2019-08-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190827222753/https://deadline.com/2019/04/santa-clarita-diet-canceled-netflix-three-seasons-1202602903/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 劇情 ==
已婚夫婦席拉和喬爾是[[聖塔克拉利塔|聖塔克拉利塔]]的房地產仲介，某天他們的生活突然來了一個巨大黑暗的轉彎，席拉居然變成了[[喪屍|喪屍]]，需要靠吃人肉為生。<ref name="deadline" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/822559/santa-clarita-diet-is-tv-s-latest-zombie-show-complete-with-drew-barrymore-eating-people|title=Drew Barrymore Is TV's Newest Zombie (But, Don't Call Her a Zombie)|date=2017-01-17|work=E! Online|accessdate=2017-01-22|last1=Harnick|first1=Chris|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623141807/https://www.eonline.com/news/822559/santa-clarita-diet-is-tv-s-latest-zombie-show-complete-with-drew-barrymore-eating-people|dead-url=no}}</ref>

