== 評價 ==
《小鎮滋味》獲得電視評論家普遍的好評。在[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得75%新鮮度、7.18/10分（64位評論家），影評家共識：「《小鎮滋味》有相當傑出的演員，偶發笑料，亦引人入戲，但血腥的程度未必能符合每個人的胃口。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/santa_clarita_diet/s01/|title=Santa Clarita Diet: Season 1 (2017)|accessdate=2017-02-03|work=[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001213357/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/santa_clarita_diet/s01|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，獲得了66分（滿分100分，31位評論家），屬普遍的好評。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/santa-clarita-diet|title=Santa Clarita Diet - Season 1|accessdate=2017-02-03|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|archive-date=2019-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190108014836/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/santa-clarita-diet|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在爛蕃茄整合的評論中，第2季獲得82%新鮮度、7.08/10分（11位評論家），影評家共識：「《小鎮滋味》以毫無間段的喜劇成分，與為可愛的角色－－大量－－流淌的喜愛，延續第1季的氣勢。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/santa_clarita_diet/s02/|title=Santa Clarita Diet: Season 2|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=爛蕃茄|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819224540/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/santa_clarita_diet/s02|dead-url=no}}</ref>但在Metacritic整合的評論中，其收錄的兩篇評論均只給出50分（滿分100分）的評價。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/santa-clarita-diet/season-2|title=Santa Clarita Diet - Season 2 Reviews|accessdate=2018-04-23|work=Metacritic|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718081309/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/santa-clarita-diet/season-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>

